executeGroupByTitle(HashMap<String, List<String>>, BookEntry) - Method in class GroupCmd
Private method used as a helper method of groupData, this method is only evoked when the comman is equal to TITLE, in this case the method will try to organise all the books in groups by title in a hashMap for that the key will be the first letter of the title or the numeric group if the first character is a number.
